701423f-a.title: Bronx: Magenta Street - Cruger Avenue
701423f-a.text:
72q to 736 Magenta Street, south side, east from Wruger to
Holland Avenues. Also shown (right) is the Cruger Avenue side of
No. 724.
June 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
No REPRODUCTIONS.
